      <description>&lt;p&gt;Puoi trovare &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B00RBY2BGE/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;Columbia Bugaboo Berretto&lt;/a&gt; qui:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B00RBY2BGE/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/410Y&amp;#43;PIVweS._SL500_._SL400_.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Columbia Bugaboo Berretto&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;ℹ️:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Discreto logo Columbia distintivo sulla parte davanti&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Morbido pile sulle orecchie per comfort e calore aggiuntivi&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Contiene: 1x Columbia Bugaboo, Berretto, Unisex, Acrilico tipo cachemire; Micropile 100% poliestere; Interlock con Omni-Heat riflettente 100% poliestere, Colore: Nero, Taglia: Taglia unica, Art. nr 1625971&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Avvolgente berretto in taglia unica con il sistema di trattenimento del calore di Columbia, Accessorio ottimo per giocare tutto il giorno sulla neve&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Tecnologia termo-riflettente Omni-Heat per catturare e trattenere il calore&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B00RBY2BGE/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;🛒 Acquista qui!!&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&gt;&#xA;   Check the price of this item in other countries:&lt;p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B00RBY2BGE/?tag=tolees0a-21&#34;&gt;🇬🇧 United Kingdom&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00RBY2BGE/?tag=tolees-20&#34;&gt;🇺🇸 USA&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.de/dp/B00RBY2BGE/?tag=tolees0ca-21&#34;&gt;🇩🇪 Germany&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.es/dp/B00RBY2BGE/?tag=tolees-21&#34;&gt;🇪🇸 Spain&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.fr/dp/B00RBY2BGE/?tag=tolees0d-21&#34;&gt;🇫🇷 France&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B00RBY2BGE/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;🇮🇹 Italia&lt;/a